<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Capital Catalyst™ — 2x2 Partners</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:opsz,wght@9..40,300;9..40,400;9..40,500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --bg:          #0A0A09;
    --bg-mid:      #111110;
    --bg-card:     #161614;
    --white:       #F4F2EE;
    --white-dim:   rgba(244,242,238,0.55);
    --white-faint: rgba(244,242,238,0.18);
    --rule:        rgba(244,242,238,0.1);
    --rule-mid:    rgba(244,242,238,0.06);
    --tag:         rgba(244,242,238,0.07);
    --serif:       'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
    --sans:        'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  nav {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 1.6rem 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    background: var(--bg);
    z-index: 100;
  }

  .nav-logo {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--white);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .nav-logo .mark {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-style: italic;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--white-dim);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--white); }

  .nav-cta {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--white);
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--rule-mid);
    padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover { border-color: rgba(244,242,238,0.3); background: var(--tag); }

  /* ── LAYOUT ── */
  .container { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 3rem; }

  section { padding: 8rem 0; }

  .section-rule {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .section-rule span {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--white-faint);
  }

  .label-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--white-faint);
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  h2 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(244,242,238,0.7);
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    min-height: 90vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 0 3rem 6rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--white-dim);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 8vw, 7rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.02;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--white);
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .hero-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(244,242,238,0.6);
  }

  .hero-bottom {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-top: 4rem;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--white-dim);
    line-height: 1.85;
    max-width: 420px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .hero-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .hero-links a {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--white-dim);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .hero-links a:hover { color: var(--white); }
  .hero-links a.primary {
    color: var(--white);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(244,242,238,0.25);
    padding-bottom: 0.1rem;
  }

  /* ── PHILOSOPHY ── */
  .philosophy { background: var(--bg); }

  .phil-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
    gap: 6rem;
    margin-top: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .phil-left p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--white-dim);
    line-height: 1.9;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .phil-principles {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .principle {
    padding: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-right: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .principle:nth-child(even) { border-right: none; }
  .principle:nth-last-child(-n+2) { border-bottom: none; }

  .prin-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--white-faint);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .prin-title {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .prin-body {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--white-dim);
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* ── PROCESS ── */
  .process {
    background: var(--bg-mid);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .process-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .step {
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .step:last-child { border-right: none; }

  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--white-faint);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .step-title {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .step-body {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--white-dim);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* ── PULL QUOTE ── */
  .pull {
    background: var(--bg);
    padding: 7rem 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .pull-inner {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .pull-quote {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(244,242,238,0.65);
    line-height: 1.35;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .pull-attr {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--white-faint);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* ── TIERS ── */
  .tiers { background: var(--bg); }

  .tiers-intro {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--white-dim);
    font-weight: 300;
    max-width: 500px;
    line-height: 1.85;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .tiers-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 3.5rem;
  }

  .tier {
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 3rem 2.75rem;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    transition: border-color 0.25s;
  }
  .tier:hover { border-color: rgba(244,242,238,0.22); }

  .tier.featured {
    border-color: rgba(244,242,238,0.2);
    background: #1A1A17;
  }

  .tier-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--white-dim);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    background: var(--tag);
  }

  .tier-name {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.9rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .tier-name em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(244,242,238,0.6);
  }

  .tier-price {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .price-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .price-unit {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--white-dim);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .tier-desc {
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    color: var(--white-dim);
    line-height: 1.85;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule-mid);
  }

  .tier-features {
    list-style: none;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .tier-features li {
    font-size: 0.84rem;
    color: var(--white-dim);
    font-weight: 300;
    padding: 0.6rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule-mid);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .tier-features li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .li-mark {
    color: rgba(244,242,238,0.3);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    margin-top: 0.35rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ── BUTTONS ── */
  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .btn-light {
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--white);
  }
  .btn-light:hover { background: rgba(244,242,238,0.88); }

  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--white-dim);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .btn-outline:hover { border-color: rgba(244,242,238,0.3); color: var(--white); }

  /* ── STATS ── */
  .stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    margin-top: 5rem;
  }

  .stat {
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--rule);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .stat:last-child { border-right: none; }

  .stat-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--white);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--white-faint);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .tiers-footnote {
    margin-top: 1.75rem;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--white-faint);
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  /* ── RULES OF ENGAGEMENT ── */
  .rules {
    background: var(--bg-mid);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .rules-lead {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--white-dim);
    line-height: 1.9;
    font-weight: 300;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .dos-donts {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .dos { border-right: 1px solid var(--rule); }

  .dos,
  .donts { padding: 2.75rem; }

  .col-head {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--white-dim);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule-mid);
  }

  .dos ul,
  .donts ul { list-style: none; }

  .dos li,
  .donts li {
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    color: var(--white-dim);
    font-weight: 300;
    padding: 0.65rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule-mid);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .dos li:last-child,
  .donts li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .do-mark {
    color: rgba(244,242,238,0.5);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
  }
  .dont-mark {
    color: rgba(244,242,238,0.15);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
  }

  /* ── ICP ── */
  .icp { background: var(--bg); }

  .icp-intro {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--white-dim);
    font-weight: 300;
    max-width: 500px;
    line-height: 1.85;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .icp-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .icp-card {
    padding: 2.75rem 2.25rem;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .icp-card:last-child { border-right: none; }

  .icp-label {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--white-faint);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .icp-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  .icp-body {
    font-size: 0.84rem;
    color: var(--white-dim);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* ── CTA ── */
  .cta-section {
    background: var(--bg-mid);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 9rem 3rem;
  }

  .cta-inner { max-width: 680px; }

  .cta-section h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.2rem);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cta-desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--white-dim);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.9;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    max-width: 460px;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-email {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--white-faint);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    background: var(--bg);
    padding: 2rem 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  footer p {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--white-faint);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .footer-logo {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--white-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .hero-eyebrow { animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease both; }
  .hero-title   { animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.1s ease both; }
  .hero-bottom  { animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.22s ease both; }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    nav { padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    .container { padding: 0 1.5rem; }
    section { padding: 5rem 0; }
    .hero { padding: 0 1.5rem 4rem; min-height: 70vh; }
    .hero-bottom { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    .hero-links { align-items: flex-start; }
    .phil-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    .phil-principles { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .principle { border-right: none !important; }
    .process-steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .step { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
    .step:nth-child(odd) { border-right: 1px solid var(--rule); }
    .step:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .tiers-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .dos-donts { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .dos { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
    .stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .stat { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
    .stat:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .icp-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .icp-card { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
    .icp-card:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .section-rule { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.25rem; }
    .cta-section { padding: 6rem 1.5rem; }
    footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start; padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ── NAV ── -->
<nav>
  <a href="https://2x2partners.com" class="nav-logo">
    <span class="mark">2»2</span>
    Partners
  </a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#process">Process</a></li>
    <li><a href="#tiers">Engagement</a></li>
    <li><a href="#rules">Rules</a></li>
    <li><a href="#who">Who We Serve</a></li>
  </ul>
  <a href="#cta" class="nav-cta">Begin a Conversation →</a>
</nav>

<!-- ── HERO ── -->
<div class="hero">
  <p class="hero-eyebrow">Capital Formation · 2x2 Partners</p>
  <h1 class="hero-title">Capital <em>Catalyst</em>™<br>Capital Raise<br>Acceleration.</h1>
  <div class="hero-bottom">
    <p class="hero-desc">We plug into your fundraise as a structural extension of your team — bringing network, process, and judgment to the moments that determine whether a raise succeeds or stalls.</p>
    <div class="hero-links">
      <a href="#tiers" class="primary">View Engagement Options →</a>
      <a href="#process">How It Works →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ── PHILOSOPHY ── -->
<section class="philosophy" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-rule">
      <span><span class="label-num">01</span>Philosophy</span>
      <span>Capital Formation · 2x2 Partners</span>
    </div>
    <div class="phil-grid">
      <div class="phil-left">
        <h2>Capital formation<br>is a <em>system,</em><br>not a sprint.</h2>
        <p>Most raises fail not because the company isn't fundable — but because the raise wasn't structured. Introductions happened without context. Meetings lacked follow-through. Investors received information before they were ready for it.</p>
        <p>At 2x2, we begin every engagement with an assessment. We study your story, your materials, and your network before we make a single introduction. Speed matters — but so does sequence. The right investor at the wrong moment is a missed opportunity.</p>
        <p>The structural nuances — sequencing, framing, timing, follow-up — are where raises are won or lost. We build those structures for you.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="phil-principles">
        <div class="principle">
          <span class="prin-num">01</span>
          <p class="prin-title">Assessment First</p>
          <p class="prin-body">We diagnose before we recommend. Alignment precedes outreach. Every engagement starts with a structured intake.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="principle">
          <span class="prin-num">02</span>
          <p class="prin-title">People Matter</p>
          <p class="prin-body">Capital is raised by people, not decks. We invest in relationships before we make asks. Quality over volume, always.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="principle">
          <span class="prin-num">03</span>
          <p class="prin-title">Process Matters</p>
          <p class="prin-body">Structured follow-up, feedback loops, and weekly reporting keep momentum alive and prevent opportunities from going cold.</p>
        </div>
